### 4. FLFPBattleResult Modification

**File**: `d:\UE_Projects\LFP2D\Source\LFP2D\Core\LFPGameInstance.h`

Add one field to `FLFPBattleResult`:

```cpp
// 战斗中捕获的单位列表（背叛系统触发）
UPROPERTY(BlueprintReadWrite, Category = "Battle")
TArray<FLFPUnitEntry> CapturedUnits;
```

This is zero-cost when no captures happen (empty array).

---

### 5. ALFPTacticsUnit: Add TypeID Field

**File**: `d:\UE_Projects\LFP2D\Source\LFP2D\Unit\LFPTacticsUnit.h`

Add a new property to the public section of `ALFPTacticsUnit`, alongside the existing unit stats:

```cpp
// 单位类型 ID（与 ULFPUnitRegistryDataAsset 中的键对应）
UPROPERTY(EditAnywhere, BlueprintReadWrite, Category = "Unit Identity")
FName UnitTypeID = NAME_None;

// 单位星级
UPROPERTY(EditAnywhere, BlueprintReadWrite, Category = "Unit Identity")
int32 UnitTier = 1;

// 生成 FLFPUnitEntry（用于捕获、保存等）
FLFPUnitEntry ToUnitEntry() const
{
    FLFPUnitEntry Entry;
    Entry.TypeID = UnitTypeID;
    Entry.Tier = UnitTier;
    return Entry;
}
```

Each blueprint subclass of `ALFPTacticsUnit` (placed in the level or spawned from the registry) sets `UnitTypeID` in its defaults. This is the bridge between the runtime Actor and the lightweight `FLFPUnitEntry`.

---

### 6. Battle-side Capture Tracking in TurnGameMode

**File**: `d:\UE_Projects\LFP2D\Source\LFP2D\Core\LFPTurnGameMode.h`

Add capture tracking to the existing battle game mode. This is where `ChangeAffiliation` events during battle get recorded.

```cpp
// ============== 捕获追踪 ==============

// 记录战斗中被捕获的单位（背叛转化后调用）
UFUNCTION(BlueprintCallable, Category = "Battle")
void RecordCapturedUnit(ALFPTacticsUnit* Unit);

// 获取捕获列表
UFUNCTION(BlueprintPure, Category = "Battle")
const TArray<FLFPUnitEntry>& GetCapturedUnits() const { return CapturedUnits; }

protected:
// 捕获的单位列表
UPROPERTY()
TArray<FLFPUnitEntry> CapturedUnits;
```

**File**: `d:\UE_Projects\LFP2D\Source\LFP2D\Core\LFPTurnGameMode.cpp`

```cpp
void ALFPTurnGameMode::RecordCapturedUnit(ALFPTacticsUnit* Unit)
{
    if (!Unit) return;
    FLFPUnitEntry Entry = Unit->ToUnitEntry();
    if (Entry.IsValid())
    {
        CapturedUnits.Add(Entry);
        UE_LOG(LogTemp, Log, TEXT("捕获单位: %s, 星级 %d"), *Entry.TypeID.ToString(), Entry.Tier);
    }
}
```

Modify `EndBattle` to include captured units in the result:

```cpp
void ALFPTurnGameMode::EndBattle(bool bVictory, bool bEscaped)
{
    ULFPGameInstance* GI = Cast<ULFPGameInstance>(GetGameInstance());
    if (!GI) return;

    FLFPBattleResult Result;
    Result.SourceNodeID = CachedBattleRequest.SourceNodeID;
    Result.bVictory = bVictory;
    Result.bEscaped = bEscaped;

    // 只有胜利时才传递捕获的单位
    if (bVictory)
    {
        Result.CapturedUnits = CapturedUnits;
    }

    GI->SetBattleResult(Result);

    if (CachedBattleRequest.bIsValid)
    {
        GI->TransitionToWorldMap(TEXT(""));
    }
}
```

**Integration point**: `ALFPTacticsUnit::ChangeAffiliation` should call `RecordCapturedUnit`. Modify `ChangeAffiliation` in `LFPTacticsUnit.cpp`:

```cpp
void ALFPTacticsUnit::ChangeAffiliation(EUnitAffiliation NewAffiliation)
{
    EUnitAffiliation OldAffiliation = Affiliation;
    Affiliation = NewAffiliation;

    if (NewAffiliation == EUnitAffiliation::UA_Player)
    {
        if (AIController)
        {
            AIController->UnPossess();
            AIController->Destroy();
        }

        // 记录捕获（敌人 → 玩家）
        if (OldAffiliation == EUnitAffiliation::UA_Enemy)
        {
            if (ALFPTurnGameMode* GM = Cast<ALFPTurnGameMode>(GetWorld()->GetAuthGameMode()))
            {
                GM->RecordCapturedUnit(this);
            }
        }
    }
}
```

---

### 7. Post-battle Processing in WorldMapGameMode

**File**: `d:\UE_Projects\LFP2D\Source\LFP2D\WorldMap\LFPWorldMapGameMode.h`

Add:

```cpp
